Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,DAI AND PRINCESS LEONA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dai, the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow, you're so tiny!\NTalk about undependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal family of our Papnica Kingdom\Nhas long served the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest successor, Princess Leona,\Nduring the month of her 14th birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,must partake in a ritual to receive\Nthe blessing of the Earth God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This island has\Na cave into the earth, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. There is a gigantic cave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Ritual Land we seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as this island has long been feared\Nas an island of monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,no one knows where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 50 years since a member of\Nthe royal family has undergone the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happened,\Nwhen King Romos visited Papnica,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he spoke of Dai the Future Hero\Nand Brass the Venerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you would like Dai\Nto take you to the Earth Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The monsters of Dermline Island\Nwill obey Dai, will they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Cave is a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To take the Princess there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona will one day become a Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With the magic I have taught her,\Nthere will be no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, I don't wanna. She seems rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he will be useful,\NI will gladly lend him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really safe?\NAre you sure you won't get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is my backyard!\NI can walk around it blindfolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. It's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't sleep here. Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!\NI'm actually impressed, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?! Not a single spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Sir Dai just hasn't\Nundergone a Ritual of Magic yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa wants me to be a Mage, so we did\NRituals of Magic for lots of spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So you've already bound with spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still can't use a single spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Earth Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a distinguished knife\Nof the Papnica royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Temjin gets mad\Nwhen I carry it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't use magic,\Nyou might as well have a decent weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so gloomy\Nand work on your sword skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't hold anything back,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NIt's better for everyone that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus it makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't try to spare\Nmy feelings either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iruru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An Evil Scorpion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your friend?! Get it to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not a creature\Nfrom this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic doesn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This knife is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weak point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Evil Scorpion's poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa said even\Nan Antidotal Herb can't cure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan! Hurry and call Grampa Brass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa can use\Nthe cure poison spell, Kiari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna die at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! I should've worked on\Nlearning magic harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!\NCast Kiari on the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Magic Cylinder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,dies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And never come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai washed ashore here as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, he's grown up among us.\NSo everyone is his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona has been poisoned\Nby an Evil Scorpion! We must go save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How could an Evil Scorpion show up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry and cast Kiari on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you save the Princess,\Nall of my plans will have been for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If Princess Leona dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,without a successor,\NPapnica Kingdom will be mine to rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I went ahead with this ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could say she was killed\Nby the monsters of Dermline Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were all in on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only these seven of my trusted servants\Nand Varon know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gome, summon everyone!\NLet's drive them off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Another dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a servant of the gods, yet\Nyou would kill your master out of greed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The Killing Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! The Dark Lord created\Nthe Killing Machine to kill the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it move with the Dark Lord dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's your answer, old man!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Varon's magic power is driving it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I modified this abomination after it was\Nnothing more than junk from the last war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So that it could be controlled\Nby a human's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now the ultimate creature!\NWipe them out, Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This Killing Machine was created\Nto exterminate the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pitiful magic can't harm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}IRURUR{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}/{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}DERUPA{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXPLOSION-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're underground.\NWe fell in the gigantic cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had more strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could use magic, I could heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could even get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people can't even bind with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've bound\Nwith almost every spell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's proof you have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll learn to use magic someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep whining,\NI won't like you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! Don't die! Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear you'll live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that shockwave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Varon, the Princess still lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, run! They were planning\Nto kill Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison has already\Nspread through her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs a Kiari spell or she'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Varon, hurry and kill that old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That way no one will be able\Nto save the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess is sure to die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagikurosai!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dai used magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Bagikurosai doesn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to kill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you rampage\Non this island any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Little fool! Your efforts are futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic doesn't work! And you\Nlack the strength to win with a sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way for you to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! He pierced\Nthe Killing Machine's armour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been targeting the same spot?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! The Killing Machine\Nis immune to magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a crack\Nin the Killing Machine's armour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames of the Begirama spell\Nleaked in and hit Varon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Help Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bishop Temjin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! This boy took the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me, Temjin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let a judge at Papnica hear it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth God,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Leona, priestess\Nand successor of Papnica Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,come before you to be purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So Leona really is a Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I pledge myself to the Earth God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dai. You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're okay, Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gained some confidence in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When you eventually become a Hero,\Ncome to Papnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you be my bodyguard or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Leona," not "Princess!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you treat me like a stranger,\NI won't speak to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That Bagikurosai and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagikurosai!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tons of monsters\Njust showed up in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-What a pickle.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the Dark Lord would return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That's all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we go back\Nand take care of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers can handle those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We must aim for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Dark Lord has returned,\Nthe people will need a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go visit the new Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a terrible calamity\Nthreatens Dermline Island,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a man calling himself a tutor\Nappears before Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To save the island and the world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}together with\NPopp the young Mage trainee,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai decides to undertake\Na special hard training!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Hero's Tutor"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
